				\begin{document}$\infty$\end{document}, 3.3–3.7 km, 2.1–2.2 km, 1.3–1.5 km, 1.03–1.07 km, and 0.80–0.82 km. A baseline of 13 positions within the field of view (with a potential descope to 5 positions) will be recorded, depending upon the degree of fidelity desired and the time and effort available to prepare the command sequencing for the calibration. Table 8 shows the target list for the initial calibration. Table 8
